parameters.name: property
parameters.description:
Optional for ITC/HOT , only available if you have expedia hotel.
0 = all
1 = Hotel
2 = Suite
3 = resort
4 = Vacation rental condo
5 = Bed & Breakfast
6 = all Inclusive

parameters.name: win_hot_conn
parameters.description: optional for ITC/HOT, value = connector name (hotelbeds), if 1 hotel is returned 2 times by 2 connector only keep hotelbeds

parameters.name: hot_name
parameters.description: Optinal for HOT, only return hotel that match name criteria

parameters.name: service_class
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC value  blank for economy, W for premium economy, C for business, F for first

parameters.name: seats
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC /  Return the number of seats available per segment. Set to 1 to get seat information.

parameters.name: NoOvernite
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Reject flights with an overnight. An overnight is defined as having to spend the night at a connection airport

parameters.name: NoUSA
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Reject fares involving a connection or a stop in the USA

parameters.name: directonly
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Only return direct flights

parameters.name: FlexDates
parameters.description: Optional for FLT / Return fares for other dates than the requested one. Set to 1 to receive alternate dates

parameters.name: FlexDays
parameters.description: Optional for FLT / + / - days before / after requested departure date

parameters.name: FlexMinStay
parameters.description: Optional for FLT / Flex Dates minumum stay

parameters.name: FlexMaxStay
parameters.description: Optional for FLT /  Flex Dates maximum days

parameters.name: airline
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Specific airline or group of airlines. If more than one airline, separated by /

parameters.name: no_multi_airp
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Reject fares where different airports are involved with a connection flight. For example arrive at JFK and depart from EWR. Set to 1 to reject

parameters.name: max_cnx_time
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Maximum connecting time, in minutes

parameters.name: max_overnite_cnx_time
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / Maximum overnight connecting time, in minutes

parameters.name: GDS
parameters.description: Optional for FLT/ITC / G for Galileo, S for Sable, A for Amadeus

line.content: Circus Circus Hotel, Casino & Theme Park is the best value on the Las Vegas Strip. The hallmark of Circus Circus lies under the legendary Big Top, where the world's greatest circus acts perform on the Midway Stage. A valid credit card or debit card is required upon arrival to register and a $25/night incidental deposit will be charged to guests (subject to change). *A mandatory Daily Resort Fee is payable by guests directly at the hotel for both Package and Land Only (L/O) rate plans. Resort fee includes: Property-wide high speed internet access (public spaces and in-room), unlimited local and toll free calls, airline boarding pass printing, and fitness center access for guests 18+. All features and applicable charges are subject to change.

hotel_info.description: Boasting a prime setting at the heart of the Spanish capital, this Boutique and charming hotel offers guests a convenient location in close proximity to the myriad of attractions this mesmerising city has to offer. In the hotel's vicinity, guests will find the Royal Palace, Royal Opera House, Plaza Mayor and Puerta del Sol. Gran Via Avenue and the renowned artistic triangle are also situated close by. The setting is ideal for travellers who are eager to explore the rich culture, history, entertainment venues, dining options and shopping opportunities the city has to offer. This delightful boutique hotel occupies a historical 18th century building, and has retained elements of its former style. The guest rooms feature a harmonious blend of modern amenities and elements of a bygone era. The rooms are also sound-proofed, ensuring a truly relaxing stay.

This establishment is a luxury hotel located at the entrance of Madrid coming from Barajas airport 10 kilometres away and is located in a quiet residential area and close to the city center. Next to the bus and metro station with easy access to the best areas of Madrid such as one of the worlds most famous football venues BernabÃ©u Football Stadium which is 2,4 kilometres away and the Cartagena Metro Station is just 200 m from the hotel.  Thanks to its excellent location in the city centre, with very easy access to the main attractions that the area has to offer guests will find themselves in the ideal location from which to explore the delights of the area.  Facilities in the hotel include a stylish and modern restaurant, which serves modern versions of traditional Spanish dishes, there is also a terrace and garden, and a top-floor bar with incredible views of Madrid.  Each floor of the Hotel has been created by a different international architect. Upon arrival, guests can select from a photographic catalog the room they want among those available.   The unique spacious rooms feature stylish dÃ©cor, slick furniture and a luxurious private bathroom with hairdryer.  All the rooms are thoughtfully designed and beautifully finished to ensure guests enjoy perfect comfort and convenience during their stay.

Situated directly in the city centre, opposite the Madrid Opera House and just a 5-minute walk from the fantastic Palacio Real, this small, family-run hotel occupies a century-old historical building and is the perfect setting for a truly unforgettable stay in the Spanish capital. In addition to providing modern, spacious and elegant accommodation, where guests can truly relax after a day of exploring the fantastic attractions of Madrid, the hotel is an attraction in itself, with musical evenings featuring Spanish opera singers organized regularly in the hotel's restaurant, and an in-house piano bar.

With a fantastic location close to Paseo de la Castellana, the H10 Tribeca stands in Madrid's main business district. Recently refurbished by renowned interior designer, LÃ¡zaro Rosa-ViolÃ¡n, the hotel takes its name from New York's Tribeca neighbourhood due to its marked industrial inspiration. The hotel offers 140 comfortable rooms, the modern Soho Restaurant, the Lobby Bar, a library and two Meeting Rooms.
The large, comfortable rooms at the H10 Tribeca are equipped with everything you need for a comfortable stay.
With a modern design and large picture windows, this welcoming restaurant offers a full buffet breakfast as well as a range of carefully selected Mediterranean and international dishes. You can also enjoy chilling out by taking a drink in the Lobby Bar.

This modern hotel enjoys a strategic setting in the business district of Madrid. The hotel is located close to Retiro Park, just a few minutes' walking distance away from the Puerta de Alcala. The Plaza de Cibeles and Calle Serrano can also be found nearby. Many prominent Madrid attractions can be found within easy access of the hotel. A host of shopping, dining and entertainment opportunities can be found nearby. This hotel features elegantly-styled guest rooms, where focus is placed on comfort and convenience. The hotel provides well-equipped conference space and modern technical equipment, for the convenience of business travellers. The restaurant offers delectable culinary delights, which are sure to tempt even the most discerning palate.

This wonderful hotel boasts a stunning setting, lying at the heart of the mesmerising city of Madrid. The hotel is located between the Azca and the Nuevos Ministerios districts of the city. Guests will find themselves within easy access of the Paseo de la Castellana, as well as a host of attractions, restaurants, shopping opportunities and entertainment venues. The hotel enjoys a stunning architectural design, which was the building for a former embassy. The hotel allures guests with the promise of a truly enjoyable stay. The guest rooms are beautifully designed, combining traditional and contemporary elements. The hotel affords a range of exemplary leisure and recreational facilities, ensuring a memorable city break.

Located in the heart of Madrid, on the Plaza de las Cortes, near the Prado this hotel is ideal for city tours.  Just 50m from the hotel is the nearest public transport. The city's airport can be reached within 30 minutes. This city hotel offers a spacious lobby area, reception service and conference facilities. Additionally, a cafÃ©, a cocktail bar and 2 restaurants are on guest's disposal. The comfortable rooms come with a bathroom. Further facilities include satellite TV, a minibar, and individual air conditioning. Guests may also pay a visit to the in-house gym with sauna. Breakfast may be selected from an ample buffet. Lunch and dinner may be taken Ã  la carte. Furthermore, special dietary requirements can be catered for.

Centrally located in Madrid, this luxurious hotel is surrounded by restaurants, numerous pubs and clubs, as well as boutiques and shops which are all only minutes away. The nearest airport is some 12 km away and Atocha train and metro stations are within 2 km, while the local public transport links can be found directly in front of the hotel. This contemporary city hotel offers a total of 74 rooms spread over 6 floors. The hotel's facilities include a pleasant lobby with 2 lifts, a 24-hour reception with luggage room, as well as a coffee bar. Additional facilities include Ã  la carte restaurant, a TV room, conference rooms for all kinds of events and a business corner with computers, printers and free Internet. Laundry and room services are also available. The exquisitely designed air-conditioned rooms come with an en suite bathroom and modern amenities. The signature restaurant is open for dinner and it offers Mediterranean cuisine.

An emblem of the city of Madrid, the MeliÃ¡ Madrid Princesa Hotel is a luxury hotel with elegant interior design with a contemporary and cutting edge flair. The MeliÃ¡ Madrid Princesa Hotel has been fully renovated and is the perfect option for business and leisure travellers in Madrid thanks to its excellent location in the heart of the city, its extensive and comfortable facilities, and the superb quality of its services.
With views of the Royal Palace, MeliÃ¡ Princesa is a luxury hotel located in Madrid, 8 minutes' walk from Plaza EspaÃ±a and Gran Via. It offers a gym and modern rooms with flat-screen satellite TV.The upper floors of the hotel are dedicated to The Level exclusive rooms, with panoramic views over the city or the mountains as well as specific superior services and facilities such as a wellness area or an indoor pool for adults only*. Guests can enjoy elegant and spacious rooms with pillow menu, private check-in and check-out space, Nespresso space, concierge service and high quality and exclusive bathroom amenities and toiletries, organization of activities around the city, a private area with drinks and snacks and private show cooking, press in the lounge, etc.

*To check conditions.

This charming hotel is located in the heart of Madrid. Encompassed within cultural attractions, shopping districts and fine-dining opportunities, this hotel is sure to please each individual guest. Public transport links are easily accessible from this hotel. The airport is easily accessible also, just 18 km away. Designed with an Art-Deco style, this hotel oozes modernity and poise. The guest rooms are embellished with artefacts from the 19th and 20th century, giving a tasteful flair to each individual unit. Guests can avail of the conference facilities, gym, rooftop terrace or steam bath. Breakfast is offered from the in-house restaurant, Europa Deco, in a buffet-form and delivering lunch and dinner in an Ã  la carte fashion. Whether guests are travelling for business or for pleasure, this hotel is sure to enthral each visitor that passes through its doors.

Located on Gran VÃ­a Avenue, this beautiful building is within walking distance of many of the city's main attractions, cinemas, theatres, and shops.
